articles.title: Kate Beckinsale finally explains why she was hospitalized for weeks - Fox News
articles.description: Months after her mysterious hospitalization, Kate Beckinsale is finally telling her fans why she was in the hospital after "a--holes" on the internet continued to comment on her weight loss.
articles.content:
